"Kolomyts E.G., Surova N.A.","Predicting the impact of global warming on soil water resources in marginal forests of the Middle Volga Region",2010,"Water Resources","37","1",,"89","101",,,10.1134/S0097807810010094,"http://www.scopus.com/inward/record.url?eid=2-s2.0-75949109530&partnerID=40&md5=df91a0968ec4e3e8a5ff9eb15ce2bd2f","Institute of Ecology of the Volga Basin, Russian Academy of Sciences, ul. Komzina 10, Tolyatti, 445003, Russian Federation","Kolomyts, E.G., Institute of Ecology of the Volga Basin, Russian Academy of Sciences, ul. Komzina 10, Tolyatti, 445003, Russian Federation; Surova, N.A., Institute of Ecology of the Volga Basin, Russian Academy of Sciences, ul. Komzina 10, Tolyatti, 445003, Russian Federation","The response of local forest ecosystems to changes in summer soil moisture content in the context of possible climate changes. A procedure for local hydrological forecasting is presented. Calculations based on prediction climate models GISS and HadCM3 for forest ecosystems on zonal ecotones between forest and steppe showed a progressive development in the XXI century of a thermoarid trend with pronounced soil drying during the vegetation period, which should result in decay of broad-leaved and mixed forests and their replacement by small-leaved-pine and oak-grove forest-steppe. © Pleiades Publishing, Ltd., 2010.","Climatic forecast; Ecological modeling and forecasting; Marginal forest ecosystems; Soil moisture reserves","broad-leaved forest; climate change; climate modeling; climate prediction; ecological modeling; forest ecosystem; global warming; mixed forest; soil moisture; summer; Russian Federation; Volga Region",,,,,,"Budyko, M.I., (1971) Klimat i zhizn' (Climate and Life), , Leningrad: Gidrometeoizdat; Zubenok, L.I., (1976) Isparenie na Kontinentakh (Evaporation on the Continents), , Leningrad: Gidrometeoizdat; Vygodskaya, N.N., (1981) Radiatsionnyi rezhim i struktura gornykh lesov (Radiation Regime and Structure of Mountain Forests), , Le